data.description: This beautiful open concept 4 bed 2 bath with 3 car garage is the SMARTEST home on the block. Green powered with 24 solar panels, includes Tesla Energy Powerwall, smart switches throughout, wifi hotspots in each room & patio. Gourmet kitchen with movable home bar, wine cooler and island. Over 50K in upgrades!  This is a must see! Cigar room complete with wood plank floors, smart control Rabbit Air Purifier with 2 extractors in the ceiling. All lighting, ceiling fans, Arlo Security cameras and 4 SMART Tv's included in purchase. Complete with water softener as well. Screened in lanai has a 20 x 20 retractable screen with greenspace and water views. Fenced property with irrigation and landscape with lighting.   Stay in and entertain, or visit the amenity center in this gated community. Do as much or as little as you choose. Visit the pool, gym, playground and/or pickleball courts. Enjoy the scenic lakes and walking paths throughout the community. Centrally located to get to the beaches with a short drive to 1-95. Set tee time at World Golf Village, or take a 20 minute ride to Historic Downtown Saint Augustine. Seller incentives for the right buyer, please listing agent for more details.
